7. Development Methodology (Beginner-Friendly 3-Month Plan)
Phase 1 ‚Äî Understanding & Planning (Week 1‚Äì2)

Study CNC processes

Understand failure reasons

Define use cases

Plan data requirements

Phase 2 ‚Äî Data Collection (Week 3‚Äì4)

Simulate CNC data

Store it in database/file

Create initial dataset

Phase 3 ‚Äî Data Engineering (Week 5‚Äì6)

Clean data

Smooth noisy values

Create features like:

rolling averages

temperature difference

vibration shift

Phase 4 ‚Äî Analytics & ML (Week 7‚Äì9)

Perform EDA

Train ML models

