Evaluate and compare models

Phase 5 ‚Äî Dashboard Development (Week 10‚Äì11)

Build Streamlit dashboard

Add graphs, metrics, alerts

Phase 6 ‚Äî Deployment & Report (Week 12)

Deploy ML model using FastAPI

Prepare blackbook & presentation

