11. Conclusion

CNCMate is an AI-powered CNC analytics platform designed to improve efficiency and productivity for small manufacturing units. By focusing on data collection, data analysis, machine learning, tool-life prediction, and dashboard analytics, this project demonstrates how AI can bring Industry 4.0 capabilities to MSMEs.

